to crate a new branch 
//git branch branchName

to swicth into branches
//git checkout existing branchName

to create a new branch directcly switch into that branch
//git checkout -b branchName


to check list of local branches
//git branch

to check list of local and remote branches
//git branch -a

to publish newly created local branch to remote repo
//git push -u origin newCreatedBanchName